        {
          "anchor": "Create-your-subscription-group",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Create your subscription group",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you plan your subscription offerings, create a subscription group, which is the container for your subscriptions. You can create your subscription group by using ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "POST /v1/subscriptionGroups",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.appstoreconnectapi/documentation/AppStoreConnectAPI/POST-v1-subscriptionGroups",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") with a payload.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Hereâ€™s an example payload:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "  \"data\": {",
            "    \"type\": \"subscriptionGroups\",",
            "    \"attributes\": {",
            "      \"referenceName\": \"Ukulele Lessons\"",
            "    },",
            "    \"relationships\": {",
            "      \"app\": {",
            "        \"data\": {",
            "          \"type\": \"apps\",",
            "          \"id\": \"6446148572\"",
            "        }",
            "      }",
            "    }",
            "  }",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "The ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "referenceName",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " field is internal and isnâ€™t displayed to users. Use a descriptive string thatâ€™s useful for your own organization and recognition purposes.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Hereâ€™s an example response, truncated for clarity:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "  \"data\" : {",
            "    \"type\" : \"subscriptionGroups\",",
            "    \"id\" : \"2000036297\",",
            "    \"attributes\" : {",
            "      \"referenceName\" : \"Ukulele Lessons\"",
            "    },"
          ],
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The response contains an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "id",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " field in the primary ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "data",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " object. You need this ID for subsequent steps.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Create-your-subscription-group-localization",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Create your subscription group localization",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Your localized subscription group name shows up in your app when a user goes through the process of reviewing or purchasing your auto-renewable subscription. To add a localization to your subscription group, you need the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "id",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " of the subscription group from the previous step.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "POST /v1/subscriptionGroupLocalizations",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.appstoreconnectapi/documentation/AppStoreConnectAPI/POST-v1-subscriptionGroupLocalizations",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") with a payload that specifies the localized name of the subscription group, the locale that youâ€™re adding, and an optional custom app name. Depending on your app and subscriptions, you might need to add many localizations. If thatâ€™s the case, you can add many in one call to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "/v1/subscriptionGroupLocalizations",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Hereâ€™s an example payload:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "  \"data\": {",
            "    \"type\": \"subscriptionGroupLocalizations\",",
            "    \"attributes\": {",
            "      \"name\": \"Ukulele Lessons\",",
            "      \"locale\": \"en-AU\",",
            "      \"customAppName\": \"The Best Ukulele Lessons\"",
            "    },",
            "    \"relationships\": {",
            "      \"subscriptionGroup\": {",
            "        \"data\": {",
            "          \"type\": \"subscriptionGroups\",",
            "          \"id\": \"2000036297\"",
            "        }",
            "      }",
            "    }",
            "  }",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you configure your subscription group, create your subscription following the steps in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.appstoreconnectapi/documentation/AppStoreConnectAPI/managing-auto-renewable-subscriptions",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
